pi-stomp (3.0-2) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Add lg, swig, python3-dev to Build-Depends so the lgpio Python wheel
    can link against liblgpio during the build.
  * Install the cached lg .deb in build.sh before invoking dpkg-buildpackage.
  * Build in a separate pi-stomp-build directory so debian/ is not copied into
    the installed source tree.

